  "texts": [
    "As shown in Fig. 2, the resulting HDF5 file contains these four types of data.",
    "Fig. 1 The sensors used for data collection during the experiment.",
    "We collected muscle activity data from both the dominant arm and dominant leg.",
    "As all participants held the racket with their dominant arm, the collected data allows us to scrutinize the muscle activity and force application timing of the racket-holding hand.",
    "We also included muscle activity data for the dominant leg based on a prior study indicating greater muscle activation in the dominant leg 86."
  ]
}